# Assets Insurance Loans Premium Funding Net Amount

## identifier
de8627

## type
float

## definition
This is, as at the relevant date, the principal amount of loans provided to an insured for the purposes of funding their premium, net of associated provisions for impairment and deferred fee income, and including any accrued interest.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.Insurance.LoansPremiumFundingNet.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo3.02.05
- period=instant
